<L>__{exterior caribbean sea day}
<A>__{elizabeth breaks the surface, looks around. and then, finally jack appears, sucking in air. he shows what he went after: his pistol. he tucks it into his shirt.}
<C>__{elizabeth}
<D>__{you went back for that? we need to head for the reef!}
<A>__{she starts swimming. jack hesitates. the black pearl is already underway; he stares at it.}
<C>__{jack}
<D>__{that's the second time i've had to watch that man sail away with my ship.}
<A>__{he turns away, and swims after elizabeth.}
